---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Construction Project Management Software | BuildWorkPro" description="Track construction projects from bid to completion with phases, tasks, Gantt charts, and team assignments. Kanban, list, and timeline views for subcontractors.">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Features</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
          Construction Project Management
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Track every project from bid award through final closeout. Organize work into phases and tasks, visualize timelines with Gantt charts, and assign your crew -- all from a platform designed for how subcontractors actually run jobs.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <!-- TODO: Restore "Start free trial" button at launch -->
          <span class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-slate-400 rounded-xl cursor-default">
            Coming Soon
          </span>
          <a href="/features/" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-slate-700 bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl transition-all">
            All features
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overview -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20">
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate mx-auto">
        <h2>Manage your jobs without the complexity</h2>
        <p>
          Generic project management tools were not built for construction. They do not understand phases, they do not connect to your bids, and they do not track the financial side of a job. BuildWorkPro gives subcontractors a project management experience that fits construction workflows -- where a "project" is a job with a contract value, a schedule, a crew, and a paper trail of pay apps and change orders.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you run three active jobs or thirty, BuildWorkPro gives you a clear view of every project's status, budget health, and schedule progress. Your team sees what they need to see. Your office staff manages the details. And your foremen know exactly what to focus on each day.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Capabilities -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center mb-12">Key capabilities</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 ring-1 ring-brand-100 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 6A2.25 2.25 0 016 3.75h2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0110.5 6v2.25a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H6a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6zM3.75 15.75A2.25 2.25 0 016 13.5h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 012.25 2.25V18a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H6A2.25 2.25 0 013.75 18v-2.25zM13.5 6a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25H18A2.25 2.25 0 0120.25 6v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 10.5h-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6zM13.5 15.75a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25H18a2.25 2.25 0 012.25 2.25V18A2.25 2.25 0 0118 20.25h-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25v-2.25z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Phases and tasks</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Organize jobs into phases like Rough-In, Trim, and Finish. Break each phase into tasks with assignees, due dates, and status tracking. Nest work the way you actually structure it on the jobsite.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 ring-1 ring-brand-100 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 4.5h14.25M3 9h9.75M3 13.5h5.25m5.25-.75L17.25 9m0 0L21 12.75M17.25 9v12" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Gantt charts</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Visualize your project timeline with an interactive Gantt chart. See phase durations, task dependencies, and schedule overlaps. Drag to adjust dates and keep your timeline current.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 ring-1 ring-brand-100 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 4.5v15m6-15v15m-10.875 0h15.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V5.625c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H4.125c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v12.75c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Kanban boards</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">View all your projects on a Kanban board organized by status -- Bidding, Awarded, In Progress, Punch List, Complete. Drag cards between columns as jobs progress.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 ring-1 ring-brand-100 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Team assignments</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Assign team members to projects and individual tasks. Track who is working on what, and ensure your foremen and crew leads have clear visibility into their responsibilities.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 ring-1 ring-brand-100 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m2.25 0H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Document management</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Attach plans, specs, submittals, and photos to any project. Keep every document organized by project and accessible to your team from one central location.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 ring-1 ring-brand-100 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Budget tracking</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">See contract value, billed to date, change orders, and remaining budget for every project. Spot margin issues early and make informed decisions about resource allocation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center mb-12">How it works</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Create a project</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500">Convert an accepted bid into a project or create one from scratch. Add the GC, location, contract value, start and end dates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Build your schedule</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500">Add phases and tasks with dates, durations, and dependencies. Use the Gantt chart to visualize the timeline and adjust as the project evolves.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Assign your crew</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500">Assign team members to the project and to specific tasks. Everyone sees their responsibilities and the project manager has a clear view of workload.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">4</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Track progress</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500">Update task statuses as work is completed. Monitor budget health, review pay apps, and handle change orders -- all from the project detail view.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <!-- TODO: Restore "Ready to get started?" CTA with trial button at launch -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Coming Soon</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 mb-8">We're preparing for launch. Internal testing in progress.</p>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-slate-400 rounded-xl cursor-default">
        Coming Soon
      </span>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
